0.33l bottle from Vinspecialisten, Randers. Pours hazy dark amber with small off-white head, that disappeared quickly. Aroma is citrus, grape fruit, hoppy and malty. Flavor is sweet, malty and hoppy. Finish is much less bitter than expected...could probably drink quite a few of these without getting hopped out. Nice beer.

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

.33l bottle. Dark amber, hazy, good off-white head. Aroma and taste is hoppy, citrus, creamy. Nice bitter finish.

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone
